  "title": "Customer Service Coordinator (Warehouse)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Provide customer service support through phone and email communication.</li>\n  <li>Prepare shipping and import/export documentation in line with SOPs, and issue invoices upon shipment closure.</li>\n  <li>Monitor shipments to ensure timely clearance and delivery.</li>\n  <li>Meet established KPIs for all inbound and outbound activities.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with supervisors on warehouse operations.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to fulfill orders and ensure on-time delivery.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate inventory records, verify stock levels, and report discrepancies.</li>\n  <li>Carry out general housekeeping tasks to uphold workplace standards.</li>\n  <li>Ensure a safe and compliant working environment.</li>\n  <li>Perform other duties as assigned by the supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
